<br />
En el segundo punto, Draghi ha dicho que han bajado el interés oficial a niveles por debajo de practicamente los que se dan en toda la zona euro. Y punto, un poco de seriedad por favor.  </div> <div class="comment-meta"> <div class="comment-votes-info">   <span >votos: </span><span id="vc-12313069" class="votes-counter">0</span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span >karma: </span><span class="votes-counter" id="vk-12313069" title="karma">6</span>   <a href="/c/12313069" title="permalink" class="permalink"></a>  </div> <div class="comment-info"> <span class="ts showmytitle nomobile" data-ts="1360786918" title="creado: "></span>  <a class="username" href="/user/mikeollie/commented" id="cauthor-38">mikeollie</a>  <img data-2x="s:-20.:-40."  data-src="http://mnmstatic.net/v_14/img/mnm/no-gravatar-2-20.jpg" src="http://mnmstatic.net/v_14/img/g.gif" class="tooltip u:228630 lazy wide" alt="mikeollie"  />  </div> </div> </div> </li><li><div id="c-39"> <div class="comment-body" id="cid-12313097">  <a href="http://www.meneame.net/story/8-grandes-mentiras-draghi-congreso-diputados/c039#c-39" rel="nofollow"><strong>#39</strong></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;  <a class="tooltip c:1842556-37" href="http://www.meneame.net/story/8-grandes-mentiras-draghi-congreso-diputados/c037#c-37" rel="nofollow">#37</a> típico  </div> <div class="comment-meta"> <div class="comment-votes-info">   <span >votos: </span><span id="vc-12313097" class="votes-counter">0</span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span >karma: </span><span class="votes-counter" id="vk-12313097" title="karma">6</span>   <a href="/c/12313097" title="permalink" class="permalink"></a>  </div> <div class="comment-info"> <span class="ts showmytitle nomobile" data-ts="1360787376" title="creado: "></span>  <a class="username" href="/user/vecinaco/commented" id="cauthor-39">vecinaco</a>  <img data-2x="s:-20.:-40."  data-src="http://mnmstatic.net/v_14/img/mnm/no-gravatar-2-20.jpg" src="http://mnmstatic.net/v_14/img/g.gif" class="tooltip u:308213 lazy wide" alt="vecinaco"  />  </div> </